name: Journey through the strings of my soul

metadata.name: Part1. Inception
metadata.description:
Part one. Inception.
There are more than four dimensions in our universe.  We know about three spatiale of time.  What is the time?  What is space?  What is reality, and do we really exist?  Or maybe somewhere in another parallel universe, there is someone who is watching us?  All these thoughts have visited each of us at least once... but what is the true reality?
